{"tid":2515740,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"艾倫由始至終都係善良嘅人","createTime":"2021-05-04T07:43:16.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-05T01:57:20.000Z","uid":320696,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"f69e985a446b782d075863ec3b530ec5f47f451a","tid":2515740,"uid":320696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T07:43:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmNX8Y692rSYWXN8pN47XDbzwgKjU2oxR7pYw1cVh9npHZ?filename=RSQS92g.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRSQS92g.jpg&h=2f16a515&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n根本壓到艾倫最後一根稻草就係塔伊巴條撚屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我覺得艾倫坐係度同萊納鳩up就係想聽埋塔伊巴個演講<br />\n<br />\n塔伊巴講到艾倫奪取始祖之力好危險<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但明明就係馬萊破壞城牆先搞到艾倫同佢老豆要奪取始祖之力 冇得怨啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n到最後塔伊巴向帕拉迪島宣戰已經冇彎轉 帕拉迪島冇咗外交一百年 又一直比人妖魔化 係個刻唔反抗已經逃唔過滅亡<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4fd31ef6d1e6949e77c829fa5b5bd3e031ff7041","tid":2515740,"uid":25494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T08:28:10.000Z","msg":"戴巴家族=艾奸"},{"pid":"c4428605b0ef9170738d8dd72b9b2539a8844cda","tid":2515740,"uid":3454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T09:00:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/Qmeconqjgj4Sd7ZBmW1P6GZ4CosUWsAaR9psoJ4zw6LgGs?filename=sCkDmH3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsCkDmH3.png&h=cb2a0f17&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n馬萊玩大咗<br />\n戴巴先出嚟幫手執屎(宣戰)"},{"pid":"752b7ccbc5772e782a29b2903f7e53bd54343b52","tid":2515740,"uid":187741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T09:03:44.000Z","msg":"我不知道.jpg"},{"pid":"6aac9abb6aa62bfd4f24014d12e965ed27bfdb46","tid":2515740,"uid":271397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0